{"tid":1147937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出手推學童頭　阿伯與勸止青年爆罵戰︰我唔係打係教","createTime":"2019-05-10T06:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T07:33:43.000Z","uid":225464,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1942c3864946300b4c0693507e76e76b2aeb7c","tid":1147937,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"出手推學童頭 阿伯與勸止青年爆罵戰︰我唔係打係教<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VYjEl1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VYjEl1&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGrTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=cc68fba9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VYjEl1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190510/photo/bkn-20190510123734494-0510_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190510135311\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190510%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190510123734494-0510_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190510135311&h=889929a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就算點都唔應該郁手嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網民周四（9日）將影片上載至Facebook群組「無敵新聞香港 － HK Club 04」，據畫面所見，阿伯怒不可遏斥謂︰「你知唔知佢兩個初頭喺洪水橋點呀&hellip;嚟到呢度當遊樂場，鍾意點玩就點玩」，又辯稱︰「我冇打佢，我推佢頭咋喎&hellip;我呢啲叫教訓佢，唔係打佢&hellip;就係你哋啲年輕人，從來都唔識教啲𡃁仔嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n惟青年不值其所為，反駁指：「你係佢邊個呀？教訓佢&hellip;用口講咪得囉，郁手！」又向疑似被推的男童詢問傷勢，惟男童只低頭挨着扶手，不發一言，並由身邊的同學安撫。"},{"pid":"bc550e753e547eec73e22b15ea1f31e2d7c260ed","tid":1147937,"uid":140319,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:46:32.000Z","msg":"使乜同佢嘈<br />\n直接打電話搵慈母<br />\n指住佢話佢普通襲擊，搞掂"},{"pid":"445e2983e85e4158fb88c637ee1f160d2c8934a0","tid":1147937,"uid":203681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:48:21.000Z","msg":"打返個廢老話幫佢死鬼老豆教仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d69303f7cbaf6d59f0fffa368dcf8d97cf8028","tid":1147937,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"咁要教下阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac